          <actionDate>2016-01-05</actionDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Mental Health Access and Gun Violence Prevention Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes FY2017 appropriations for the Department of Justice, the Department of Health and Human Services, and the Social Security Administration to: (1) increase access to mental health care treatment and services, and (2) promote reporting of mental health information to the National Instant Criminal Background Check System.</p>]]></text>
